Raycomm Transworld Industries Incsaid it has agreed in principle subject to board approvals toacquire Spiridellis Consulting Group Inc, a privately-heldcomputer services consulting firm, for a number of commonshares to be determined based on pretax earnings of Spiridellisover a five-year period.    The company said it will gaurantee that almost all of theissued shares will attain price levels ranging from five tonine dlrs each for two years after their issuance.    It said Spiridellis had revenues of 3,500,000 dlrs incalendar 1986. Reuter&#3;